N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 19 ยง 156.5 - Reconsideration procedure

State Regulations

An applicant may request reconsideration of any rejection of
a proposed name, upon written request addressed to the secretary and marked to
the attention of the Director of the Division of Corporations. The applicant
shall attach to his request a copy of the rejection, and include a statement of
the reasons upon which the applicant seeks approval of the
name. Notes
